kr/125239520/in/set-909995/" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nima_flickr/125239520/in/set-909995/" rel="nofollow">[8]</a>) taken in Shiraz in the spring of 1932 (1311 <a href="/wiki/Iranian_calendar" title="Iranian calendar">AH</a>).</dd>
</dl>
